text: Double or Nothing (2022) was a professional wrestling pay-per-view show made by All Elite Wrestling (AEW). It took place on May 29, 2022 at T-Mobile Arena in Las Vegas suburb of Paradise, Nevada. It was the fourth Double or Nothing event held by AEW. The main event saw CM Punk defeat "Hangman" Adam Page to win the AEW World Championship.
